quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  28,29,"Mi ifukk Musa tallit, u iseyyeê akked twacult is, iwala times ar tama n udrar. Inna i twacult is: \"qqimet, wala$ times, ahat ad awen d awi$, segs, asali ne$ asafu, amar a ppesseêmum"
  28,30,"Mi ibbwev $uôes, ipwanced ed si ttejôa, di rif ayeffus n te$zut, deg umviq iôqan: \"a Musa! S tidep, Nek d Öebbi, Mass imavalen"
  28,31,"Veggeô taâkwazt ik\". Mi p iwala, la tesseêôiîiw amzun d azrem, ibren ur iwexxeô. \"A Musa! Qeddem, ur ppagwad, aql ak, ih, di laman"
  28,32,"Err afus ik di loib ik, a d iffe$ d amellal, ur ihlik. Sseqôeb ed $uôek i$il ik, ad ak tekkes tugwdi. Tigi d sin n ppbut s$uô Mass ik, i Ferâun akked imvebbôen is. Ih, nitni d agdud iballa$en"
  28,33,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Nek n$i$ yiwen segsen, ugade$ ad iyi n$en"
  28,34,"Gma Harun yif iyi afeûûeê umeslay. Azen it id yidi d amâiwen, ad iyi tebbet. Nek ugade$ ad iyi nekôen"
  28,35,"Inna: \"a Nesseohed tayepp ik s gma k. Ad awen Nefk, i sin, adabu; ur kwen id ppawven. S issekniyen nne£, d kunwi akked wid iddan yidwen ara irebêen"
  28,36,"Mi ibbwev $uôsen Musa, s issekniyen iberrzen, nnan: \"ayagi, siwa ssêur id innulfan. Ur nesli s waya, $uô ibabaten nne$ imezwura"
  28,37,"Inna Musa: \"Mass iw Iéôa sennig wiyav, anwa iwumi Ifka nnhaya s$uôeS, anwa ara d igwrin deg Uxxam. Imednas, s tidep, ur rebêen"
  28,38,"Inna Ferâun: \"a yimvebbôen, ur awen mli$ ara kra n ôebbi, war nekkini. Ecâal iyi times ar talaxt, a Haman; bnu yi lbeôo aâlayen; ahat ad ali$ ar ÖÔebbi n Musa. Nek, s tidep, êesbe$ t seg wid iskiddiben"
  28,39,"Neppa, akked iâsekôiwen is, sme$wôen iman nnsen di tmurt, war ssebba. £ilen, ar nitni, ur d ppu$alen $uône£"
  28,40,"Neppa, akked iâsekôiwen is, Neîîef iten. Nger iten ar yill. Wali amek tevôa d imednas"
  28,41,"Nerra ten d imeqwôanen i ineccden ar tmes. Ass n tnekra, ur ppusellken"
  28,42,"Neqqen asen xezzu di ddunit agi. Ass n tnekra, nitni seg ucmiten"